  "description": "<i>Avalon</i> is a timed puzzle board game, a variation of Rubik's Cube. The goal of the game is to arrange an identical pattern in the second window before the time runs out.  The player can move each row in the cube to the left, right, down and up. Solving the task allows uncovering one part of prize picture. The screen is divided into three parts. The bottom part shows the information (remaining time, level code). Right window shows a pattern, which must be repeated in the left window. ",
